{"commits":["46f896224d1a2d9f3c5c65a9874ee9344e1ae7bc"],"user_facing":true,"description":"**Staleness policy.** Discovery registry entries now carry verify callbacks; set_discovered uses them to retain values that still exist on disk when a re-scan omits them.","type":"feature"}
