{"commits":["ffbbe4507fc28a25297e03783742ad6d487dfb50"],"user_facing":true,"description":"**Deferred discovery apply.** Slow discovery results for the focused segment are now buffered and applied on defocus, preventing option list disruption while the user is interacting. A pending indicator (*) appears in the segment label when results are waiting.","type":"feature"}
